    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Previously only available through <i>Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number Digital Special Edition,</i> the Jacket Character Pack for PAYDAY 2 is now available as a standalone DLC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This DLC includes all of the collaborative items from <i>Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number</i> and the<i> Digital Special Edition:</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Jacket Character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sociopath Perk Deck</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Masks (6 from the <i>Hotline Miami 2 Mask Pack, Richard Returns</i>, <i>Richard Returns Begins</i> plus the <strong>brand new</strong> <i>Mega Richard Returns</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Secondary Weapon (<i>Jacket's Piece</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Melee Weapon (<i>Carpenter's Delight</i>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Weapon Mods</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All items are still attainable from owning <i>Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number (Hotline Miami 2 Mask Pack) and Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number Digital Special Edition (All other items)</i> on Steam, OR this DLC. </p>",
